title: John Cena and Roman Reigns wage war of words | FRIDAY NIGHT SMACKDOWN | WWE ON FOX
author: WWE ON FOX
description:
John Cena and Roman Reigns met face to face on Friday Night SmackDown, just eight nights before facing each other for the Universal Championship at SummerSlam. The Head of the Table and 16-time World Champion stepped into the squared circle and made violent intentions for the match clear.
